name: Lala in the void - grayscale cameras
description:
"Lala in the void," 2022, 1920x1080 MP4 video, 15s
This piece is inspired by the "Nymphs in the digital void" series of paintings that I am currently working on.  I imagine that each and every one of us has a void inside us, or even several voids.  In my void I imagine a universe where trickster Nymphs play. See more at www.laladrona.com
